data.description: Enjoy the bright open floor plan this BEAUTIFUL HOME has to offer along with some amazing features including: NEW ROOF in 2018, on demand water heater AND water filtration system, FENCED PLUNGE POOL, RV Parking, NEW glass shower doors, STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, cozy living room space with a fire place to enjoy during the winter nights, and so much more. For those needing some extra space or a shop, the garage is fully insulated and climate controlled with a mini split! This home is a must see with it's amazing custom touches! The home is located just minutes from great restaurants/shopping and down the street is Enterprise Park/Kids Kingdom. Don't miss out on this charming East Redding home in a HIGHLY desirable neighborhood.
